episodes.title: #23 Shiny Happy People 😀
episodes.description: I watched all episodes of the new series shiny happy people and this is my opinions of the first 2 episodes, I never was a fan of 19 kids and counting and now I’m really not but I am proud of the girls for speaking and the ex members for sharing their stories. Let me know if you all would like a part 2 💜

episodes.title: 4 moms and 44 siblings
episodes.description: Calvin shared what it was like growing up in the polygamous cult known as “the work” a branch off from the FLDS.

episodes.title: #21 How the Order steals from loyal followers 💴 💰 🏠
episodes.description: In the episode we hear Deward Robert Peterson tell the story of his mother who was a dedicated Order member and the sad truth of how she was treated, some believe Ortell treated her poorly because he hated that she left him and found another man to marry.

episodes.title: Therapy session with Priscilla
episodes.description: Come hang out with us while we trauma dump 😂 my cousin Priscilla is coming back to YouTube! In this episode she tells why she left and what she has been dealing with.

episodes.title: #18 The Women of my CULT(Modern day Handmaids)
episodes.description: In this episode I discuss all the similarities that an order woman from my cult and a handmaid from the show “A Handmaids Tale” there are so many shocking similarities and I didn’t even get through all of them, I hope you guys enjoy and have a happy holiday season 💜

episodes.title: Polygamy makes NO SENSE!!! #17
episodes.description: I was unhinged…I apologize in advance

episodes.title: #16 Are we attracted to a chaotic life? 🔥
episodes.description: In this episode I asked the Culty Crew for advise on struggling with depression and feeling guilty for being happy as well as almost being attracted to a life of chaos, I loved all the advice and I hope it helps more than just me today :) 💜

episodes.title: #15 Healing and progressing with my sister Kami
episodes.description: Kami and I…Laugh a lot in this episode lol we talk about those uncomfortable times that actually push us to grow as well as why things are taboo AND we get the Culty Crews comments 🥰

episodes.title: Julli Robinson
episodes.description: Julli shares her experience being born in the Order and married as the 7th wife to The Cult leaders oldest son, we get to hear about her book that she is writing “The Cult Wall” and so much more! Huge thank you to Julli for sharing so much

episodes.title: Tom Green (Creepy Story From my CULT)
episodes.description: Let’s talk about the Sh!t show that is Tom Green…from marrying his own step daughters to trying to court his teenage sons girlfriend 🙃 but it’s ok because it’s all in the name of the LORD 🙏 come along with me(if I had to watch it then so do you 😆)

episodes.title: Creepy Story From my CULT 👻 (Val plays with spirits 💀)
episodes.description: In the episode…we get kinda off topic 😆 we hear about the man in Val’s closet, his first kiss and how his home became a brothel without his knowledge 😵 join us on our random spooky banter 👻🍁💀🎃⚰️

episodes.title: Creepy Story from my CULT (Allison plays with a OUIJA board)
episodes.description: In this episode, Allison talks about playing with a Ouija board while she was in the order and the strange events that happened after. She tells us of a grave with the numbers “666” and “killed by the beast” carved in to it. Who was the best? Why was it there?

episodes.title: Creepy story from my CULT (Planet Neophrates🌓)
episodes.description: Let’s talk about how “Brother Ortell Kingston” (my grandpa and the 2nd Cult leader of the order) met “Krishna Venta” (another cult leader from planet Neophrates 🪐), after meeting in the military they both decided to build KAYS CROSS ✝️ in Kaysville Utah. LETS TALK ABOUT IT the weird beginning and the sudden ending to Krishna’s life by his own followers.

episodes.title: How to know you’re in a Toxic relationship 💔
episodes.description: I am not an expert in psychology BUT I did take some classes AND I grew up in a cult surrounded with toxic behaviors and now that I have been out 9 years, I am very well aware of what was toxic and what is healthy and would LOVE to share what I have learned with you and I LOVE to hear what you all have learned in your life experience as well💕 leave it in the comments on my YouTube! Love you guys and I really hope this podcast can help in some way💕 remember to KNOW YOUR WORTH and just because someone else does not value you DOES NOT mean you are not valuable!!!

episodes.title: Leah
episodes.description: In this episode Leah and I discuss the contention between the LeBaron polygamist cult and the AUB (the group Leah escaped) resulting in a murder, Leah gives details on members and what it was like inside the Apostolic United Brotheren GO SUBSCRIBE TO HER YOUTUBE!!!

episodes.title: Bloom where you’re planted 🥀
episodes.description: This episode I asked you all your favorite quotes and why and YOU PULLED THROUGH! I love all of these quotes and learning more about the Culty Crew🥰love you all and if there is a quote you want to share that we missed, comments are welcome on the YouTube video of this episode #7🥰love you guys and see you Sunday☕️

episodes.title: One CULT to the next 🛐
episodes.description: Eskel joins us as we discuss his belief on Mormon rules and dating different women of different beliefs as well as atheists, astral projection, and the Akashic records 📕 ⭐️ 🌙
subjects: The Church Of Jesus Christ Of Latter-Day Saints

episodes.title: Mom is in a CULT
episodes.description: This Episode you guys get to be my therapist lol I am trying to process all of this in a healthy way and put up boundaries in a healthy way and I have been so exhausted trying to figure out the best way possible…so I figured let’s process it together…A lot of us go through this and I think as adults we have to change our relationship from child and Parent to Adult and Parent…IDK I am still learning and I am open to hearing any of your ideas as well💜love you guys and see you on Sunday Culty Crew💜 💜 💜

episodes.title: Michelle/Ava
episodes.description: Trigger warning! There is a lot of talk of abuse in this episode that may be very triggering…we discuss sexual abuse, marital rape etc. please do not listen if this will trigger you. I am very glad we were able to discuss these things and feel healthy enough mentally process them…there was a time where I would have a panic attack trying to explain my abuse and for anyone who is struggling with this and is a minor in the order 801-253-5720 is a number to Utah Sandy DCFS you can call and make an anonymous report if you or someone you know is a minor being sexually abused.

episodes.title: Product of a Cult
episodes.description: In this Episode, my little brother Eskel and I discuss how pedophilia is glorified in the order. Later on in the episode our older sister Kami joins as we discuss getting death threats and what we believe happens when we die….this one may be triggering so please use caution when starting this episode

episodes.title: INTRO to the Culty Crew Pod
episodes.description: Hello! This is the introduction to my podcast and what you can expect in future episodes💜hoping to cover a lot more deep topics that make us all think💜would love to hear your feedback on my YouTube pod episode comment box as well 💜love you Culty Crew!!!

episodes.title: Jessica/Stephanie
episodes.description: Jessica joins me as we discuss the hardest escape on Escaping Polygamy and Jessica tells where she got her new name and left her old name Stephanie behind.
